Key Features:

Sleek Design: Our analog clock boasts a sleek and minimalist design that enhances readability and visual appeal.

Real-Time Updates: Using JavaScript's Date object, the clock displays the accurate current time, updating in real-time without the need for page refresh.

Smooth Animations: Enjoy smooth, second-by-second rotations of the clock hands, providing a seamless and immersive user experience.

Customizable Styles: The clock's appearance is highly customizable. Modify the CSS to change colors, sizes, and styles, tailoring it to fit seamlessly into any web project.

Lightweight and Responsive: Built with performance in mind, this clock is lightweight and responsive, ensuring optimal user experience across various devices and screen sizes.
